  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dba\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbb \u0dc0\u0dc4\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Hospital workers block fuel",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Puttalam Base Hospital staff including doctors were waiting in line to get fuel but the Puttalam-Kurunegala road was closed in front of the hospital this afternoon (24th).",
        "A group of staff from the Puttalam Base Hospital had gone to the Sirambiadiya petrol station due to the Friday being set aside to refuel the hospital staff, but no petrol had been dispensed by noon.",
        "When inquired about this from the petrol station he has stated that although he has taken the relevant action so far, no petrol has been provided.",
        "However, a group of staff including doctors who had gone to the Sirambiadiya petrol station to fetch petrol could be seen waiting for the fuel to arrive at the scene.",
        "The nurses and other medical staff who had remained in the hospital until the afternoon to protest the non-delivery of petrol had to be temporarily discharged from the hospital due to a lack of response.",
        "However, due to the lack of an answer, a group of hospital staff closed the Puttalam-Kurunegala road in front of the hospital.",
        "Due to the closure of the road, the police had taken steps to divert the traffic from the alternative routes."
      ],
